  <h3>Introduction</h3>
  <p>
    This implementation guide supports checking of HL7 AU profile metadata, as detailed in the wiki:
    <ul>
      <li>
        <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/hl7au/au-fhir-base/wiki/HL7-AU-Conventions:-profile-and-extension-metadata">HL7 AU Conventions: profile and extension metadata</a>
