  <a name="technical"></a>
  <h3>FHIR validator use</h3>
  <p>
    This command can be used to validate all HL7AU resource profiles:
  </p>
  <pre>
java -jar validator.jar 
-version 4.0.1 
-ig https://robstwd.github.io/fhir-ig-experiment-01/package.tgz 
-profile "https://about.me/robeastwood/fhir/ig/StructureDefinition/structuredefinition-hl7au-sdf-1"
au-fhir-base/resources/au-*.xml</pre>

